  "lore": "Clad in Cataphractii plate and unleashing hails ofSwarmer or Breaker missiles from their armour mounted rocket launchers, these implacable warriors are fortress-breakers of unparalleled skill. The bleak spectacle of these warriors upon the battlefield, surmounting any obstacle before them, became synonymous with Perturabo’s wrath unleashed. Recruited from amongst the most battle-hardened Iron Warriors, Tyrant Siege Terminators are expected to brave the most ferocious enemy fire without regard for their own survival - even more so than others of their grim brotherhood they understand the mathematics of war.",
